+# Yoga Class Booking App
+
+A Flutter application for browsing and booking yoga classes.
+
+## Architecture
+
+This app follows a clean architecture pattern with the following components:
+
+### Models
+- `yoga_class.dart`: Represents a yoga class with details like name, type, description, etc.
+- `class_instance.dart`: Represents a specific instance of a yoga class on a particular date.
+- `booking.dart`: Represents a booking made by a user.
+- `cart_item.dart`: Represents an item in the shopping cart.
+
+### Services
+- `firebase_service.dart`: Handles all interactions with Firebase Firestore.
+
+### Providers (State Management)
+- `class_provider.dart`: Manages the state of yoga classes, including filtering.
+- `booking_provider.dart`: Manages the shopping cart and user bookings.
+
+### Screens
+- `home_screen.dart`: Displays a list of available yoga classes with filtering options.
+- `class_detail_screen.dart`: Shows detailed information about a specific yoga class.
+- `cart_screen.dart`: Displays the user's shopping cart.
+- `checkout_screen.dart`: Handles the checkout process.
+- `bookings_screen.dart`: Shows the user's booking history.
+
+### Widgets
+- `class_card.dart`: Card widget for displaying a yoga class in the list.
+- `filter_bar.dart`: Widget for filtering yoga classes by day and time.
+
+## Features
+
+1. **Browse Yoga Classes**
+ - View a list of available yoga classes
+ - Filter classes by day of the week
+ - Filter classes by time of day (morning, afternoon, evening)
+
+2. **View Class Details**
+ - See detailed information about each class
+ - View upcoming class instances
+ - Add class instances to cart
+
+3. **Shopping Cart**
+ - Add classes to cart
+ - Remove classes from cart
+ - View cart total
+
+4. **Checkout**
+ - Enter email address
+ - Complete booking
+
+5. **Booking History**
+ - View past bookings
+ - See details of booked classes
+
+## Firebase Integration
+
+The app connects to Firebase Firestore to:
+- Fetch yoga class data
+- Fetch class instance data
+- Store and retrieve bookings
+
+## State Management
+
+The app uses the Provider package for state management, with two main providers:
+- ClassProvider: Manages yoga class data and filtering
+- BookingProvider: Manages cart and booking functionality","refToolCallId":"toolu_01PT2U3yiC7bt4FRB3eoc3F9"},{"type":"text","text":"Let's update the main README.md file for the project:"},{"type":"toolCall","toolCallId":"toolu_01P6aeVQSqPiSRVAvWZyja3f","statusText":"Viewed file","status":"SUCCESS","context":{"files":[{"path":"comp1786cw/README.md","fsPath":"/Users/macmini/AndroidStudioProjects/comp1786/comp1786cw/README.md"}]},"isHidden":false},{"type":"toolCall","toolCallId":"toolu_01REEE4RVzquAcYGi63VWhpa","statusText":"Change generated","status":"SUCCESS","context":{"files":[{"path":"comp1786cw/README.md","fsPath":"/Users/macmini/AndroidStudioProjects/comp1786/comp1786cw/README.md"}]},"isHidden":false},{"type":"codeHunk","lineBasedDiff":"--- comp1786cw/README.md
